hadiths[20]{hadithnumber,text}:
1701,"Hazrat Suwaid bin Ghafla (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main eik safar mein Hazrat Zaid bin Suhaan aur Salman bin Rabeea (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke sath tha, mujhey eik chaabuk mila ( jo maine utha liya ( to un dono ne mujh se kaha ke usey phenk dey . maine kaha : nahin. agar uska Malik mujhey mil gaya to (usey de-dun ga) warna is se fayda uthaaoonga. phir main hajj ke liye gaya aur Madiney bhi aaya to maine Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal kiya, unhoney kaha : mujhey eik thaili mili thi jis mein sau Dinar they, to main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya, aapney farmaya : ''eik saal tak uska aelan karo.'' chunanche main eik saal tak uska aelan karta raha. phir aap ke paas aaya, to aapney farmaya : ''eik saal (aur) aelan karo.'' maine eik saal aur uska aelan kiya. phir aap ki khidmat mein aaya, aapney farmaya : ''eik saal (aur ( aelan karo.'' maine eik saal mazeed uska aelan kiya. phir main aap ke paas aaya aur arz kiya ke maine koi aisa aadmi nahin paya jo isey janta ho. to aapney farmaya : ''inki ginti ko yaad rakho, iski thaili aur sarband bhi . agar iska Malik aa jaey to behtar , warna in se fayda uthao.'' (Salma bin Kabeel ne ( kaha : mujhey nahin maloom ke ''aelan kerney ka hukm'' teen baar diya ya eik baar."
1702,Shoba ne mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kiya (is mein hai aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( farmaya : ''eik saal tak uska aelan karo.'' aapney ye baat teen dafa kahi. (Salma bin Kuhail ne) kaha mujhey nahin maloom ke uska mafhoom eik saal mein teen baar aelan karna tha ya teen saal tak aelan karna .
1703,"Salma bin Kuheil ne apni sanad se usi ke ham-maani bayan kya aur aelan ke baarey mein kaha : '' do saal ya teen saal .'' aur farmaya : '' uski ginti kar lo , uski thailii aur uska sar band khoob yaad rakho .'' mazeed kaha : '' phir agar uska Malik aa jaey aur uski ginti bata dey aur thailii ka sarband bhi to uskey hawaley kar dena . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye alfaz yani ''agar wo unki ginti bata dey '' sirf Hammad ki riwayat mein hain."
1704,Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se giri padi cheez ke mutalliq sawal kiya to aapney farmaya : ''eik saal tak uska aelan karo. phir uska sarband (bandhan) aur thaili (ya bartan jis mein wo ho) khoob yaad kar lo. aur usey apney istimal mein ley aao. agar uska Malik aa jaey to usey dey do.'' phir usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! gum shuda bakri (ke baarey mein kya irshad hai?) aapney farmaya : ''usey ley lo. ye tumharey liye hai ya tumharey bhai ke liye ya bhediye ke liye.'' kehney laga : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aur gumshuda oont? is par aap ghussay mein aa gae yahan tak ke aap ke rukhsaar surkh ho gaey ya kaha ke chehra surkh ho gaya. aur farmaya : ''tumhen us se kya gharz? uskey sath uska joota (paon) hai aur mishkeeza hai. (uskey pet mein pani zakhira kerney ki gunjaaish aur salahiyat hai) yahan tak ke uska Malik aa jaeyga.''
1705,"Janab Malik ne is hadees ko isi sanad se usi ke ham-maani riwayat kiya. aur mazeed kaha : ''(uskey sath) uska mishkeeza hai, wo pani par pahunch kar pani pi lega aur jhaadiyaan kha kar guzaara kar lega.'' aur gumshuda bakri ke silsiley mein (خذها) ''usey ley lo'' ke lafz riwayat nahin kiye aur giri padi cheez (luqta) ke baarey mein farmaya : ''eik saal tak iska aelan karo. phir agar iska Malik aa jaey ( to behtar ( warna tum jano (yani uskey Malik bin jao).'' aur  ''kharch kar leney.'' ka zikr nahin kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : usey Sauri , Sulaiman bin Bilal aur Hammad bin Salma ne Rabeea se usi ke jaisi riwayat ki aur unhoney (خذها) ka lafz nahin kaha."
1706,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se giri padi ashiya (cheezon) ke mutalliq puchha gaya to aapney farmaya : ''eik saal tak uska aelan karo. agar uska talab kerney wala aa jaey to usko dey do, warna uski thaili (ya bartan) aur uska sarband yaad rakho , phir usey kha lo ( apney istimal mein ley aao ( iskey baad agar uska mutalaashi (khoji) aa jaey to uskey hawaley kar do.''"
1707,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sawal kiya gaya. aur Rabeea ki hadees ke manind zikr kiya. (sabiqa hadees : 1704) kaha ke aap se giri padi cheez ke mutalliq sawal kiya gaya to aapney farmaya : ''eik saal tak uska aelan karo. isliye agar uska Malik aa jaey to uskey supurd kar do. nahin to uska bandhan aur bartan khoob yaad kar lo aur usey apney maal mein shamil kar lo. phir agar uska Malik aa jaey to usko dey do.''"
1708,"Yahya bin Saeed aur Rabeea se Quteba ki sanad se usi ke ham-maani marwi (bayan) hai. is mein izafa hai : ''agar uska mutalaashi (khoji) aa jaey aur uski thaili (ya bartan) aur uski ginti ( waghaira alaamaat ( bata dey to wo cheez uskey supurd kar do. aur Hammad ne bhi Ubaidullah bin umr sey, unhoney Amr bin Shuaib sey, unhon (Amr) ne apney walid (Shoaib) sey, unhoney apney dada ( Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas ( sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se isi ke jaisi riwayat ki.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Hammad bin Salma ka ye izafa, jo unhoney Salma bin Kuheil , Yahya bin Saeed , Ubaidullah bin umr aur Rabeea ki riwayat mein zikr kiya hai yani ''agar uska Malik aa jaey aur us chiz ki thaili (ya bartan) aur uska sarband (alaamaat) bata dey to usey uskey hawaley kar do.'' (is sanad ke sath ( ye alfaz mehfooz nahin hain. yani ( فعرف عفاصها ووكاءها (aur Aqba bin Suwaid ki hadees jo unke walid se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se marwi (bayan) hai ke ''eik saal tak aelan karo.'' isike sath Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees mein bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se marwi (bayan) hai ke ''eik saal tak aelan karo.''"
1709,"Hazrat ayaaz bin Himaar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisey koi giri padi cheez miley to usey chahiye ke eik ya do aadil gawah bana ley. aur chupaey nahin aur na ghayeb karey, phir agar uskey Malik ko paey to usey lauta dey , warna wo Allah ka maal hai jisey chahta hai inayat farma deta hai.''"
1710,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya ke) darakhton par) lataktey phal ka kya hukm hai? aapney farmaya : ''jis kisi zarurat mand ne usey apney munh se kha liya ho, apney pallu mein kuchh na baandha ho to us par kuchh nahin. lekin jo wahan se kuchh lekar nikley to us par do guna jurmaana hai aur saza. aur jisney usey uskey makhzan mein aa janey ke baad churaya to agar wo dhaal ki qeemat ke barabar hua to is par haath katey ga.'' aur gumshuda bakri aur oont ke baarey mein wesay hi bayan kiya jaisey ke doosrey raawiyon ne zikr kiya hai. aur giri padi cheez ke baarey mein puchha gaya to farmaya : ''jo tumhen aabaad raston aur bastiyon mein se miley to uska eik saal tak aelan karo. isliye agar uska dhoondney wala aa jaey to uskey hawaley kar do, warna wo tumhari hai. aur jo kisi ujaad wiran jagah se miley to us mein aur aisey hi koi dafeena miley, to us mein khums hai.'' ( paanchwan hissey Zakat hai.)"
1711,Amr bin Shuaib ne apni usi (mazkura baala) sanad se is hadees ko riwayat kiya aur gum shuda bakri ke baarey mein uskey lafz hain ( فاجمعها ( ''yani usey apni bakriyon ke sath mila lo.''
1712,"Amr bin Shuaib ne isi sanad se riwayat kiya. aur gumshuda bakri ke silsiley mein kaha : ''ye terey liye hai ya terey bhai ke liye ya bhediye ke liye, usey le-le aur bas.'' aur isi tarah us riwayat mein Ayub aur Yaqoob bin Ata ne Amr bin Shuaib sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se (فخذها) ka lafz bayan kiya hai."
1713,"Ibne Is'haq , Amr bin Shuaib sey, wo ( Amr ( apney walid sey, wo apney dada ( Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ( sey, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se yehi riwayat kartey hain to unke lafz hain : (فاجمعها حتى يأتيها باغيها) ''usko apney maal ke sath mila ley yahan tak ke uska mutalaashi (khoji) aa jaey.''"
1714,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ko eik Dinar mila. wo usey Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke paas ley aaye, Hazrat Fatima ne uskey baarey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha to aapney farmaya : ''ye Shan Wale Allah ka rizq hai.'' chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam), Hazrat Ali aur Hazrat Fatima ne us se kha liya. iskey baad aap ke paas eik aurat aai jo eik Dinar dhoondti phir rahi thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Ali ! wo Dinar ada kar do.''"
1715,"Bilal bin Yahya Absa Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se naqal kartey hain ke unhen eik Dinar mila , to unhoney us se aataa kharida , aatey waley ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko pehchan liya to usney Dinar unko wapis kar diya. to Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne wo ley liya aur us mein se do qeeraat kaat kar unka gosht kharida."
1716,"Janab Sehal bin Saad ka bayan hai ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan (ghar mein) aaye to (dekha ke) Hasan aur Hazrat Husain ro rahey hain. puchha ye kyon ro rahey hain? kaha ke bhook ki wajeh se ro rahey hain. isliye Ali (ghar sey) nikal aaye to (ittifaq sey) baazar mein unhen eik Dinar pada mil gaya to wo Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aaye aur bataya (ke is tarah se mila hai). unhoney kaha : falan yahudi ke paas jaeyn aur hamarey liye aataa ley ayen. chunanche wo yahudi ke paas aaye aur us se aataa kharida . yahudi ne kaha : bhala aap us shakhs ke daamaad hain jo apney aap ko Rasulullah kehta hai? unhoney kaha : haan ! to usney kaha : Dinar apney paas rakhen aur aataa ley jaeyn . Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) wahan se chaley aur Hazrat Fatima ke paas (aataa) ley aaye aur sari baat batai . unhoney kaha : falan qassaab ke paas jaeyn aur eik dirham ka gosht ley aaen. chunanche wo gaey, apna Dinar uskey paas rehan rakha aur eik dirham ka gosht ley aaye. Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne aataa goondhaa , handiya choolhey par rakhi , roti pakaee aur apney walid (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bula bheja. wo unke yahan tashrif ley aaye. to Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main aap ko bataun agar aap isey halal farmaen to ham isey khaen gey aur aap bhi hamarey sath khaen gey aur iska haal is  tarah se hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sun kar farmaya : ''Allah ka naam lekar khao.'' chunanche sab ne kha liya. abhi wo apni jagah (dasterkhaan hi) par baithey they ke eik ladka , Allah aur Islam ka wastey de-kar apna gumshuda Dinar dhoondta phir raha tha. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hukm diya aur usey bulaya gaya. aapney us se puchha to usney kaha : mujh se baazar mein (kahin) gira hai. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Ali ! us qassaab ke paas jao aur us se kaho ke Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmatey hain : wo Dinar merey yahan bhej do aur tumhara dirham merey zimmey hai.'' chunanche usney Dinar bhej diya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey us ghulam ke hawaley kar diya."
1717,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamein chhadi, rassi, kudra aur is qisam ki chizen utha leney ki rukhsat di thi ke insan un se fayda utha ley. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke isey Nauman bin Abdussalam ne Mughira (bin Muslim) Abu-Salma se apni sanad se riwayat kiya hai. aur Shababa ne Mughira bin Muslim sey, unhoney Abu-Zubair sey, unhoney Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya hai. (kaha ke wo log chhadi , kudra waghaira utha leney mein koi harj na samajhtey they) aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka zikr nahin kiya. (mauquf bayan kiya hai.)"
1718,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''gumshuda oont pakadney wala agar chhupa ley to us par jurmaana hai aur (mazeed) uskey sath uska misl bhi.''"
1719,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Usman Taimi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hajiyon ki giri padi cheezen uthaane se mana farmaya hai. Ahmed ne riwayat kiya ke ibne-Wahab ne kaha : ''haaji ki cheez padi rehney di jaey yahan tak ke uska Malik usey pa ley.'' ibne Muhab ne ( apni sanad mein ) (عن عمرو) kaha hai. (أخبرني عمرو) nahi kaha.
1720,Munzir bin Jarir kehtey hain ke (main apney walid) Jarir  (bin Abdullah Al Bajli (Raziallahu anhu)) ke sath bu-azeej maqam mein tha ke charwaahaa gayen lekar aaya. aur un main eik gaey unki nahin thi. Hazrat Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha : ye kya hai? usney kaha : bas gaayon ke sath mil gaee hai. hamein maloom nahin ke kis ki hai. to Hazrat Jarir ne kaha : usey alehda kar do. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai : ''gum shuda chiz ko koi (ضال) ''gumrah insan'' hi leta hai.''
